{"tid":1560521,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"熱愛日本文化嘅香港愛國畫師貓尾繪Twitter發表示威者破壞言論","createTime":"2019-09-11T08:34:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T12:17:43.000Z","uid":285253,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"20868fe219165a23ef8c77eb09e73abf81012a27","tid":1560521,"uid":285253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T08:34:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QfkM6Dp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQfkM6Dp.jpg&h=4f7336ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kK9mVwL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkK9mVwL.jpg&h=8025760f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d79VfwL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd79VfwL.jpg&h=954749e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zC6c2bL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzC6c2bL.jpg&h=3f226f3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7NWDXK5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7NWDXK5.jpg&h=c9951826&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RcPRyir.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRcPRyir.jpg&h=28a23cd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MgNvORM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMgNvORM.jpg&h=9e35f1cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n7v1VwN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn7v1VwN.jpg&h=56bebd02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n事情尋日開始係Twitter發酵後再係Facebook被廣傳<br />\n呢位叫猫尾みどり(100%香港人) 既畫師<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/midori_draw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmidori_draw&d=33lQL0pOg%2F%2Bbj%2F%2FH3PrIWRD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=5a694d7d\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/midori_draw</a><br />\n於Twitter表示示威者好噁心, 剩係識搞破壞, 見到想嘔!!!<br />\n愛國畫師經常周遊列國由其愛好日本文化<br />\n但都不忘一顆愛國心<br />\n相信咁矛盾既心情一定受盡良心責備先導致只敢係Twitter同用日文發聲<br />\n<br />\n但人地放眼既係大灣區市場, 怕咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nInstagram有成68.8K followers架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/nekoo_draw/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fnekoo_draw%2F&d=33lQL0pOg%2F%2Bbj%2F%2FH3PrIWRD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=26b69717\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/nekoo_draw/</a><br />\n名可以改, 但畫風就真係唔係一時三刻可以啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比人追擊到Facebook專頁:<span style=\"color: red;\">貓尾繪</span>都關閉埋避下風頭<br />\n而家只係剩返Youtube channel同Pixiv<br />\n<br />\n<strong>以下更新由網友提供<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\nYT(轉左名Pi Cat+del哂片): <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCbG6608XFR2Gze9c-APSPHw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCbG6608XFR2Gze9c-APSPHw&d=33lQL0pOg%2F%2Bbj%2F%2FH3PrIWRD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=fce6e5a1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCbG6608XFR2Gze9c-APSPHw</a><br />\npixiv: <a href=\"https://www.pixiv.net/member.php?id=251261\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pixiv.net%2Fmember.php%3Fid%3D251261&d=33lQL0pOg%2F%2Bbj%2F%2FH3PrIWRD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=3dfb3c69\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.pixiv.net/member.php?id=251261</a><br />\n<br />\n發夢得知好似係當<span style=\"color: red;\">紅</span>畫師資料<br />\n潘X屏 (Cat Poon)<br />\n已婚<br />\n工作洽商請電 9496 6676<br />\n櫻井姬子為陳年舊名 / Cosplay藝名<br />\n曾於Bossini打工 , 後黎轉行成功好proud of幫日本老細打工,老細個女仲好欣賞自己既畫風添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n興趣係會自誇老公神似日本著名男性聲優兼歌手神谷浩史見稱<br />\n成名作品: 2019年9月8日於Twitter發表示香港威者剩係識攪破壞 , 見到都好想嘔 <br />\n<br />\n人地爭取緊五大訴求既時候你係度奶緊大灣區居民既春袋喳<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">勿忘7.21白衣人恐襲、831太子站事件、<br />\n警暴濫權、黨鐵可恥</span></strong></strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">「五大訴求、缺一不可」</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"ab1c7cd4d9b280c824a57ab73bef31691bd4add0","tid":1560521,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T08:39:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f187c8046b88cf5f74ed66bb0cc2d78ff4006758","tid":1560521,"uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T08:55:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f588b28ff883d5f8702d2644832f6a3076e14ffb","tid":1560521,"uid":71085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:20:44.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n唔擺去動物台？吹水台好影沉"},{"pid":"4e3a0dc53e1c21c0f7655212a2965e100d5d0303","tid":1560521,"uid":71085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f588b28ff883d5f8702d2644832f6a3076e14ffb","tid":1560521,"uid":71085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:20:44.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n唔擺去動物台？吹水台好影沉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:21:35.000Z","msg":"易*"},{"pid":"722cd29ecd39d53590f53dbb094933efb31678bf","tid":1560521,"uid":262054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:21:56.